                            <comment id="15851856" author="sergey_beryozkin" created="Fri, 3 Feb 2017 18:11:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the patch, I&apos;ve applied it with the minor updates - the same code should work with another setRequestUri overload, the raw values should be set to preserve the encoded chars if any for JAX-RS Encoded annotations to work, and I only resetting a query if the new one is not null - it is not clear yet if resetting the existing queries with a possible null is expected&lt;br/&gt;
thanks&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15862536" author="nhtzr" created="Sat, 11 Feb 2017 21:10:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi. I noticed that this fix can also be applied to the 2.7.x and 3.0.x branches.&lt;br/&gt;
Could it be possible to add it to those branches?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15863538" author="sergey_beryozkin" created="Mon, 13 Feb 2017 11:59:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi, 2.7.x is not supported, while I recall I had difficulties with back-porting the fix to 3.0.x, I&apos;ll check again a bit later on &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
